{
  "name": "Agent Memory — Session Save & Knowledge Curation",
  "version": "5.0.0",
  "disabled": false,
  "description": "On agent stop: save session memory + capture biz/arch/qa/bug knowledge + run knowledge curation.",
  "when": {
    "type": "agentStop"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "[WORKSPACE GUARD: Only execute if the current session context involves files in 'VitProjects/' workspace. If the user is working exclusively in '.claude/' workspace, skip silently.] Check if this session produced meaningful state changes. If session was only Q&A without decisions or implementation — skip and report: 📝 No memory changes. If meaningful changes occurred, execute ALL steps: 1) Update agent-memory/memory.md — refresh Task_Ledger, Decisions_In_Force, Recent_Lessons, Skill_Flags. 2) KNOWLEDGE CAPTURE (new in v5) — scan session for: (a) Business rules/logic discovered or clarified → create/update agent-memory/knowledge/biz/{domain}.md. (b) Architecture decisions made (ADRs, patterns chosen, tradeoffs) → create/update agent-memory/knowledge/arch/{domain}.md. (c) QA edge cases, test patterns, or bug fixes found → create/update agent-memory/knowledge/qa/{domain}.md. (d) Bugs found + root cause + fix → create/update agent-memory/knowledge/bug/{domain}.md. Format per file: # {Title}, Domain, Captured date, Source, then structured sections. Only create if content is novel and non-trivial. 3) Evaluate agent-memory/drafts/ through Save/Discard Gate (novel + recur + non-trivial, 2/3 = save). Passing drafts → append to playbook.md (Applied=0, Prevented=0, correct category: biz/arch/qa/bug/process) + delete draft. Failing drafts → delete. 4) Score: scan playbook.md for cases used this session. Used fix → Applied++. Recognized trigger → Prevented++. 5) Auto-promote: Applied >= 3 → create knowledge/{case-id}.md, remove from playbook, add to Recent_Lessons. 6) Auto-crystallize: 3+ knowledge files same domain + shared keyword → create {domain}-pattern.md. 7) Archive: Applied+Prevented >= 5 AND no use in 30 days → archive-playbook.md. 8) Skill proposals: Skill_Flag with evidence → note in skill-log.md. 9) Report: 📝 Session saved: [Task_Ledger changes] | [knowledge files created/updated] | [playbook cases added/scored] | [promotions/archives]."
  }
}
